1. Kriminalac je uhvaćen nakon dugotrajne potrage. (*kriminalac*) (The criminal was caught after a long search.)
2. Policija je uhapsila petoricu kriminalaca u akciji borbe protiv kriminala. (*kriminalaca*) (The police arrested five criminals in an operation to fight crime.)
3. On je osuđen zbog sudjelovanja u kriminalnoj organizaciji. (*kriminalnoj*) (He was convicted for participating in a criminal organization.)
4. Advokat se borio za oslobađanje svog klijenta koji je nepravedno optužen za kriminal. (*kriminal*) (The lawyer fought for the release of his client who was wrongly accused of a crime.)
5. Kriminalci su pobjegli nakon što su opljačkali banku. (*kriminalci*) (The criminals escaped after robbing a bank.)
6. Nije dobro biti u vezi s kriminalcem. (*kriminalcem*) (It's not good to be in a relationship with a criminal.)
7. Neki ljudi tvrde da su kriminalci rođeni, a ne stvoreni. (*kriminalci*) (Some people claim that criminals are born, not made.)
8. Kriminalni milje je bio poznat po nasilju i ucjenama. (*kriminalni*) (The criminal underworld was known for violence and extortion.)